Title name:

Healthcare Symptom Checker and Guidance Agent

Problem Statement:

Patients often seek preliminary guidance on symptoms before consulting healthcare professionals, but existing tools lack personalized, conversational interaction.

Steps:

Collect symptom-disease mappings and medical guidelines from trusted sources.

Design the Al agent to take symptom descriptions and ask clarifying questions.

Use the agent to provide possible causes and recommended next steps.

Ensure the agent communicates in clear, patient-friendly language.

Validate the agent's responses with sample symptom inputs.

Data Requirements:

Symptom-disease mappings, medical guidelines, and FAQs from trusted healthcare source CDC or WHO datasets.

Expected Output:

A conversational agent that outputs possible diagnoses and recommended actions in natu language text.

Generate prompt based on data given so that windsurf can make a perfect website that fulfills the requirement

